name: Cookie Clicker Debug
description: This Is The Debug Version Of The Game!!! You Have Access To Developer Console To Change Values Of The Game. Codes: (8197 - Reset Everything) (100C - Give 100 Coins) (10C - Give 10 Coins) (50C - Give 50 Coins) (2K - Give 2 Keys) (5K - Give 5 Keys) (10K - Give 10 Keys) (10P - Give 10 Points) (50P - Give 50 Points) (100P - Give 100 Points) (200P - Give 200 Points) (500P - Give 500 Points)  (1000P - Give 1000 Points) (2500P - Give 2500 Points) (5000P - Give 5000 Points) All Codes Are Case Sensitive!!!
